{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.880", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.120", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.040", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Ministerin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.440", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich halte Ihre sicherheitspolitische Agenda f\u00fcr ein Sicherheitsrisiko."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.000", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Zweite, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.520", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was Ihre bisherige vierj\u00e4hrige Amtszeit kennzeichnet\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.560", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich habe nicht den Eindruck, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.640", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das besser wird\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.840", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist ein unverantwortlicher Umgang mit Steuergeld. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.560", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zu diesem Punkt will ich als Erstes etwas sagen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.880", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben heute wieder gesagt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.120", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie viele Jahre lang wie viel Geld gek\u00fcrzt worden ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.160", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie viel gespart worden ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.160", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was Sie heute nicht gesagt haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.400", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.800", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich will das noch einmal in Erinnerung rufen\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.520", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Verteidigungshaushalt in den letzten vier Jahren um 20\u00a0Prozent gestiegen ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.240", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Verteidigungshaushalt hat inzwischen ein gr\u00f6\u00dferes Volumen erreicht\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.360", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "er wird in dieser Legislaturperiode weiter wachsen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.840", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als jeder andere Verteidigungshaushalt in den letzten Jahren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.400", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "20\u00a0Prozent Steigerung in vier Jahren\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.480", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "andere Haushalte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.400", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.280", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "w\u00fcrden sich \u00fcber solche Wachstumsraten freuen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.200", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt schauen wir einmal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.120", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was Sie mit diesem Geld gemacht haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.400", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben ja in dieser Woche den R\u00fcstungsbericht vorgelegt bekommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.360", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich will zwei Beispiele nennen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.640", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das erste Beispiel ist das Projekt Eurofighter. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.560", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Eurofighter ist wahrscheinlich zw\u00f6lf Jahre sp\u00e4ter fertig als geplant und kostet 6,7\u00a0Milliarden Euro mehr. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.240", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das zweite Beispiel ist der A400M. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.000", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er ist wahrscheinlich elf Jahre sp\u00e4ter fertig als urspr\u00fcnglich geplant und kostet 1,2\u00a0Milliarden Euro mehr. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.120", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.880", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie reden hier gerne \u00fcber Haushaltsdisziplin und die schwarze Null. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.840", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Beim Verteidigungshaushalt scheint das alles kein Problem zu sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.840", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich halte das f\u00fcr unverantwortlich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.080", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Ministerin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.400", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie reden gerne \u00fcber Trendwenden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.480", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich w\u00fcrde mich \u00fcber die Trendwende hin zur Sparsamkeit im Verteidigungsetat freuen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.960", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das w\u00e4re einmal ein echter Fortschritt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.360", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich m\u00f6chte noch eine Bemerkung zum Thema Sicherheitsrisiko machen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.680", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben auf die Friedensdividende der 90er-Jahre hingewiesen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.560", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben auch darauf hingewiesen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.560", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich die Sicherheitslage ver\u00e4ndert habe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.160", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sp\u00e4testens seit 2014. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.840", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu will ich Folgendes sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.680", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Gro\u00dfprojekte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.120", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcber die ich gerade gesprochen habe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.880", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber auch andere wie zum Beispiel der Puma\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.480", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir k\u00f6nnten die Liste fortsetzen\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.640", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diese Gro\u00dfprojekte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.600", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die so unendlich ins Geld gehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.160", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wurden lange vor dieser sicherheitspolitischen Ver\u00e4nderung geplant und in Auftrag gegeben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.200", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu einer Zeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.200", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als wir uns noch \u00fcber die Friedensdividende gefreut haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.160", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sind nicht das Ergebnis einer ver\u00e4nderten sicherheitspolitischen Lage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.440", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern wurden lange vor dieser Ver\u00e4nderung geplant. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.080", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Also begr\u00fcnden Sie diese Projekte bitte nicht mit einer ver\u00e4nderten sicherheitspolitischen Lage."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.800", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Letztlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.920", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.960", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "stellt sich die Frage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.600", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob wir wieder in eine Periode kommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.960", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der wir uns wieder \u00fcber eine Friedensdividende freuen k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.280", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nat\u00fcrlich ist es richtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.160", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass nicht nur die \u00adNATO-Staaten ihre Milit\u00e4retats hochfahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.200", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch China, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.520", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Russland und andere Staaten dieser Welt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.640", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es stellt sich doch die Frage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.240", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie wir das beenden wollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.280", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich glaube nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.640", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir das beenden k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.640", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "indem wir alle immer so weitermachen und noch mehr drauflegen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.160", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.920", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass irgendjemand den ersten Schritt unternehmen und sagen muss: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.560", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir k\u00fcrzen unseren Verteidigungsetat; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.560", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir machen bei dieser Spirale nicht mit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.280", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wir die Einzigen in diesem Hause sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.560", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die das fordern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.280", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sage ich: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.400", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Noch sind wir die Einzigen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.760", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.440", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.560", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege H\u00f6hn.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.000", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als letztem Redner erteile ich das Wort dem Kollegen Dr.\u00a0Reinhard Brandl f\u00fcr die CDU/CSU-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
}